      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/9/3/8/2",
      "text": [
        ": ذكرت إسماعيل عند أبي عبد الله عليه السلام فقال: لا والله لا يشبهني ولا يشبه أحدا من آبائي"
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.ammaar-muslim": [
          "2. [2/125] Kamal al-Diin: al-Hasan b. Ahmad b. Idris – may Allah be pleased with him – from his father from Muhammad b. Ahmad al-Ash`ari from Ya`qub b. Yazid and al-Barqi from Ahmad b. Muhammad b. Abi Nasr al-Bazanti from Hammad from Ubayd b. Zurara who said: I mentioned Ismail to Abi Abdillah عليه السلام so he said: no by Allah – he does not resemble me or any one of my forefathers."
        ]
      }
    },
